### Education

Wayne attended&nbsp;**Lafayette Elementary School**, Colorado.

Wayne then studied at&nbsp;**Eleanor McMain Magnet School**, New Orleans, Los Angeles. But dropped out at the age of 14 to focus on his music career. Finally, he attended&nbsp;**Marion Abramson Senior High School**.

He also enrolled himself in&nbsp;**University of Houston**&nbsp;in January&nbsp;2005&nbsp;but dropped out during the same year due to a conflicting schedule.

Wayne also majored in&nbsp;psychology from the&nbsp;**University of Phoenix**&nbsp;by taking&nbsp;online courses.

### Occupation

Rapper, singer, songwriter, record producer, record executive, author, entrepreneur

