### Girlfriend / Spouse

Lil Wayne dated –

  1. **Antonia Toya Carter**&nbsp;(1996-2006)–Lil Wayne married&nbsp;**Antonia Toya Carter**&nbsp;on Valentine’s Day of 2004.Lil Wayne met her in 1996 while Carter was in middle school. The couple also had a child (daughter) named, Reginae (b. 1998), i.e. when Wayne was 15. This was Wayne’s&nbsp;**1st child**. Their relationship started in 1996 and went till 2006.
  2. [**Meagan Good**](https://healthyceleb.com/meagan-good-height-weight-body-statistics/22252)&nbsp;(1998-2001) – Meagan’s first love, Lil Wayne met her in March 1998, when the two were doing a show in LA. They dated ON and OFF until March 2001.
  3. [**Lauren London**](https://healthyceleb.com/lauren-london-height-weight-body-statistics/72473)&nbsp;(1998-2009) – Lauren and Wayne started dating in July 1998. Their relationship was a kind of ON again and OFF again relationship. The duo engaged on November 10, 2007, and separated in 2009. During these 3 years, they had a child (son) named, Cameron Carter (b. September 9, 2009). This was Wayne’s&nbsp;**3rd child**.
  4. **Nivea**&nbsp;(2002-2010) – Lil Wayne started dating singer Nivea in February 2002. On December 11, 2002, Lil Wayne engaged with her. The couple was planning to marry on March 9, 2004, however, Wayne called off the engagement in 2003 to engage Antonia Johnson. The duo started dating again in 2008. She also proposed to him shortly after, but he rejected. Later, in September 2008, Lil Wayne proposed her and she readily accepted it. He was able to have another child (his&nbsp;**4th child**) named, Neal (b. November 30, 2009). Wayne’s&nbsp;**2nd child**&nbsp;was&nbsp;Dwayne III (b. October 22, 2008 at Christ Hospital in&nbsp;Cincinnati). They separated in March 2010.
  5. **Adrienne Williams-Bosh**&nbsp;(2004-2009) – She is a homemaker. Adrienne and Wayne dated from May 2004 to January 2009.
  6. **[Trina](https://healthyceleb.com/trina-height-weight-body-statistics/42874)**&nbsp;(2005-2007, 2012) – The rappers Trina and Wayne dated ON and OFF from May 2005 to May 2012. The couple were engaged in 2005 and also expecting a baby in 2006, but Trina miscarried it. They separated in September 2006, then got back together for a&nbsp;couple of months in 2007, and finally dated very briefly in 2012.
  7. **Sarah Bellew**&nbsp;(2005-2009) – He started dating&nbsp;Vietnamese radio personality, Sarah Bellew in July 2005, after meeting at one of his concerts. She gave birth to Lil Wayne’s second child, Dwayne Michael Carter on October 22, 2008. The couple engaged in July 2009. They finally called it quits in December 2009.
  8. [**Solange Knowles**](https://healthyceleb.com/solange-knowles-height-weight-body-statistics/49795)&nbsp;(2006-2008) – Singer Solange Knowles and Wayne dated from July 2006 to August 2008.
  9. **Farrah Franklin**&nbsp;(2007-2008) – From September 2007 to February 2008, he was romantically linked to another singer Farrah Franklin.
 10. [**Karrine Steffans**](https://healthyceleb.com/karrine-steffans-height-weight-body-statistics/61440)&nbsp;(2008-2013) – He started dating a writer, Karrine in early 2008 and continued dating her till December 2013.
